\par O come, let us worship and fall down before Christ Himself, our King and God. 
\par }\pard\plain \s20\qc \li0\ri0\widctlpar\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f1\fs32\cf13\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\insrsid11929813\charrsid13440266 Psalm 5
